+// Path: <replay_db>/<test_hash>/<chip_model>/<os>/<os_version>/
+//         <driver>/<driver_version>/<dpr>/
+//
+// All segments come from switches supplied by Bifrost — BlutVine never
+// constructs or infers hardware values itself.
+//
+// OS is derived from the UA string via GetPlatformFromUA() from 002.
+// Segments are sanitized to be filesystem-safe.
